<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">

<meta
name="viewport"
content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>BlogSpace</title>

<%- include('./partials/head.ejs') %>

</head>

<body>

<%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>

<div class="container">

<div class="hero card">

<h1>
Welcome to
<span style="color:#9D6638">
BlogSpace
</span>
</h1>

<p>

Create, publish and share beautiful blogs with a clean,
minimal interface inspired by the Upins design language.

Read articles from other creators, post your own stories,
and interact through comments—all in one place.

</p>

<div class="button-group">

<a href="/user/login">

<button class="btn">

Login

</button>

</a>

<a href="/user/signup">

<button class="btn-outline btn">

Create Account

</button>

</a>

</div>

</div>

<div
class="grid section-space">

<div class="card">

<h3 class="blog-title">

Write

</h3>

<p class="blog-desc">

Create articles with images and rich descriptions using a
minimal distraction-free interface.

</p>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3 class="blog-title">

Discover

</h3>

<p class="blog-desc">

Browse blogs written by other users and enjoy a modern,
clean reading experience.

</p>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3 class="blog-title">

Connect

</h3>

<p class="blog-desc">

Leave comments, interact with creators, and build your own
community inside BlogSpace.

</p>

</div>

</div>

<footer>

<p>

© BlogSpace • Built with Express, MongoDB & EJS

</p>

</footer>

</div>

</body>

</html>